body:
#README

 In Install Dlib on PC with Qt and MingW.md article, I will show you guys how to install Dlib (C++ library) on your PC, using QT and MingW compiler. Before start, you should download Dlib, Qt, cmake and MingW( Qt has already been included).



I will load video on youtube  once I complete the processing.
